Why didn't you tell us?

545
00:38:11,205 --> 00:38:14,709
My gosh, Mr. Kim! You made it!

546
00:38:14,792 --> 00:38:16,168
-Thank you for coming.
-Hello.

547
00:38:16,669 --> 00:38:18,170
Gosh, Mr. Hwang!

548
