My goodness,
you didn't have to bring anything.

563
00:39:23,611 --> 00:39:24,987
Su-chan.

564
00:39:25,071 --> 00:39:27,114
-Show Mr. Hwang around.
-Right.

565
00:39:27,698 --> 00:39:29,283
I'll be right back. Wait here, okay?

566
